    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "pCAxu",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 0,
      "name": "React + Tailwind Implementation Spec",
      "width": 520,
      "height": 1180,
      "fill": "#F7F1DF",
      "cornerRadius": 24,
      "stroke": {
        "thickness": 1,
        "fill": "#D8A84B"
      },
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 18,
      "padding": 28,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "e5KDE6",
          "name": "specNote",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 520,
          "content": "React + Tailwind implementation spec\n\nMobile-first structure:\nHeroPoster -> ServiceCards -> ProcessSteps -> LeadForm -> CTAFooter. Desktop is an lg adaptation, not the source layout.\n\nTokens:\nbg #071412 / panel #0B1C19 / card #102A25 / gold #D8A84B / text #FFF2D2 / muted #B7A982.\n\nCTA contract:\n1. Написать менеджеру в Max\n2. Написать менеджеру в Telegram\n3. Оставить заявку: messenger, contact, topic, message.\n\nAnimation:\nGold sweep on hero, staggered cards, subtle CTA glow, form focus glow, reduced-motion fallback."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "puCuf",
          "name": "specTitle",
          "fill": "#071412",
          "content": "Implementation spec",
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 34,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bJRSL",
          "name": "specIntro",
          "fill": "#2C332F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Mobile-first React + Tailwind design notes for AntEx lead magnet landing.",
          "lineHeight": 1.35,
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Nsiwt",
          "name": "specTokens",
          "fill": "#071412",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Tokens\n--bg-ink #071412\n--bg-panel #0B1C19\n--gold #D8A84B\n--gold-soft #F3D48A\n--text-main #FFF2D2\n--text-muted #B7A982\nFonts: Playfair Display headings, Funnel Sans body, IBM Plex Mono captions.",
          "lineHeight": 1.45,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "XEyJU",
          "name": "specComponents",
          "fill": "#2C332F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Components\n1. HeroPoster: logo, headline, subhead, trust badges, CTA stack.\n2. ServiceCard: icon, title, description.\n3. ProcessStep: number + concise action.\n4. LeadForm: messenger select, contact, topic, message.\n5. CTAFooter: Max, Telegram, application fallback.",
          "lineHeight": 1.42,
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "VKtGm",
          "name": "specAnim",
          "fill": "#2C332F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Animation\n- Hero: gold sweep across logo/headline on load, 900ms ease-out.\n- Cards: staggered reveal, translateY 18px to 0, opacity 0 to 1.\n- CTA: subtle gold glow pulse, disabled with prefers-reduced-motion.\n- Background: slow grain/parallax shimmer, no layout shift.\n- Form focus: gold border + soft shadow transition.",
          "lineHeight": 1.42,
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "yeSjp",
          "name": "specTailwind",
          "fill": "#2C332F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Tailwind rules\nUse CSS variables in :root for colors only. No inline styles. Build mobile layout first; desktop switches cards/process/form to grid/flex rows at lg. Use semantic anchors for Max/Telegram placeholders and a standard form submit action.",
          "lineHeight": 1.42,
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "qZM9Y",
          "name": "specA11y",
          "fill": "#2C332F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Accessibility\n- CTA labels explicit: Написать менеджеру в Max / Telegram.\n- Maintain contrast over dark background.\n- Form labels always visible.\n- No emoji flags as critical content.\n- Reduced motion fallback required.",
          "lineHeight": 1.42,
          "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
