      "children": [
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "CMqXe",
          "name": "animNote",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 640,
          "content": "Animation storyboard\n\nGoal: premium, restrained motion. Guide attention without crypto-hype noise.\n\n01 Hero entrance: logo fade+scale 0.96 to 1, headline rises 14px, gold shimmer mask, 700-900ms ease-out.\n\n02 Service cards: scroll reveal with opacity 0 to 1, translateY 18px to 0, 90ms stagger.\n\n03 CTA attention: primary Max button has slow 3.2s glow pulse; hover/press scale 0.98 and brighter gold.\n\n04 Form focus: focused field border becomes bright gold with soft inner glow. Invalid state uses clear text, no shake.\n\n05 Accessibility: prefers-reduced-motion disables shimmer, pulse and parallax; keep simple opacity fade only."
        },
